text: The 1965–66 Austrian Cup was Austria's nationwide football cup competition. LASK were the defending champions. In the first round, the first league clubs had to play away. In the event of a draw, overtime + replay, in the event of a draw in the replay, overtime + drawing of lots.Austria Soccer == Round of 32== First round with teams from the first and second league.
